Packages 
Package Description
fms_server
This is the main package for the FMS Server Contains all the code to run the server
fms_server.dao
Contains all the source code for Data Access Objects Creates an interface with MySQL database to modify databases
fms_server.handlers
Contains all the handlers used by the server, will interact with the http exchange and services the server provides
fms_server.models
Contains all database access object models.
fms_server.requests
Contains request code, these hold information about requests that are made to the server
fms_server.results
Contains all the results generated by our services, the handlers will convert them to http responses
fms_server.services
Contains all services provided for by the server.
